node_modules/
*.log
.env
commands/*.txt
banned_ips.txt
refresh-token.json
stories/*
.entities/
# Data dir: ignore everything except the config files versioned on purpose.
# shared/ (secrets) + state/ (runtime) + per-instance config stay local to each
# checkout; only the files explicitly re-included below are tracked (these were
# already versioned before the split). See docs/.../2026-06-16-data-dir-split-design.md
data/*
assets/my_voice.wav
assets/apk/
**/dist/
prompts/*
**/__pycache__/
# Nuxt build artifacts
**/.nuxt/
**/.output/